# Instructions:
# 1. Create a new integration at https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
# 2. Copy the "Internal Integration Token" and paste it as NOTION_TOKEN
# 3. Create a database in Notion with the following properties:
#    - title (Title)
#    - slug (Text) 
#    - status (Select: published, draft)
#    - description (Text)
#    - tags (Multi-select)
#    - publish_date (Date)
#    - cover (Files & media)
# 4. Share the database with your integration
# 5. Copy the database ID from the URL and paste it as NOTION_DATABASE_ID